"""Type stub for the compiled `_feldspar` PyO3 extension (WO-01/WO-02).

`ty`/mypy cannot introspect a native extension module, so this stub is
the one home for its public shape; keep it in lockstep with
`crates/feldspar-py/src/lib.rs`'s `_feldspar` module registration."""

